name: Footprint - Bamboo Charcoal Performance Socks
description:
Footprint - Bamboo Charcoal Performance Socks

Bamboo Charcoal is a new type of nano technology , the fabric in this sock is permanently embedded with bamboo charcoal.

Bamboo Charcoal is antibacterial and anti fungal.

Bamboo Charcoal emits far infrared rays and negative ions which penetrate the skin and increase oxygen delivery to cells which is known to invreace cellular function and can reszkt in less foot fatigue and faster recovery times.

name: Footprint - Painkiller Socks - Bamboo Charcoal Edition
description:
Footprint - Painkiller Socks - Bamboo Charcoal Edition

Shinners are now optional….you don’t need to get them anymore. Simply you can spend all your time focusing on your tricks, not on pain. 
These special Footprint socks are embedded with ARTIFICIAL CARTILAGE FOAM, the world’s most impact absorbing material.

They look and feel like normal socks but when the board hits the ankle bone or the shin, you’re good.

Bamboo Charcoal Edition is a new type of nano technology , the fabric in this sock is permanently embedded with bamboo charcoal.

Bamboo Charcoal is antibacterial and anti fungal.

Bamboo Charcoal emits far infrared rays and negative ions which penetrate the skin and increase oxygen delivery to cells which is known to invreace cellular function and can reszkt in less foot fatigue and faster recovery times.

name: Footprint - Tourmaline - Knee Sleeve
description:
Footprint - Tourmaline - Knee Sleeve 
with Kingfoam Joint Protection

When "karate rolling" away from a failed attempt or simply falling to the ground, the side of the knee often takes impact which soon leads to soreness, bruises and injury.

Footprint Knee Sleeves have:
ARTiLAGE (Artifical Cartilage Foam) stitched into these vulnerable areas which absorbs up to 90% of impact energy and will keep the sides of your knees protected.

- Knee Stabilization
- Assits your knee´s alignment
- One size fits most
